Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.51,0:01:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第六十三话\N许愿萤火虫的传说\N等待某位剑客的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于回到自己家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.00,0:02:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没变…   一切都如往昔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.57,0:02:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不出那就是经历了\N足以改变日本激烈战斗的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.81,0:02:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心哥哥 好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.55,0:02:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好白耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.25,0:02:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 洗得很白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.65,0:02:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 小姐 今晚的菜是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.42,0:02:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊势虾？还是鲷鱼？\N鳗鱼的话我勉强忍受啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不中用得让人想哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.93,0:02:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是那样爱敲诈\N一点长进也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.37,0:02:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样算是\N学得二重极的男人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这与那是两回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.91,0:02:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再回京都去修行吧  佐之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.14,0:02:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这臭小鬼\N竟然爬到我头上来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.18,0:02:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.61,0:02:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之你们俩先来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.55,0:03:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听好了\N佐之助请你先修理这面墙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.22,0:03:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是去京都之前你破坏的\N一直没有修补
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.83,0:03:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 墙壁是斋藤那家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别喽嗦那么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦 你跟我大扫除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长久没人在家 到处都是灰尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.91,0:03:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必需在今天\N用抹布擦全屋子一百次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.94,0:03:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一百次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.21,0:03:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰 衣服洗完了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心你来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇特的竹刀呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是钓竿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.40,0:03:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钓竿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的 剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为长途旅行的关系\N现在手头很拮据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你去钓来今夜的菜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.58,0:04:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你的喽 剑心 钓大尾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.88,0:04:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被迫做这么多工作\N肚子一定饿得慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.95,0:04:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不钓来两三只鲸鱼\N我绝不原谅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.26,0:04:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.24,0:04:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 这个家的时间\N还停留在那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.57,0:05:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋 我没学过钓鱼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心哥哥\N什么时候能钓到鲸鱼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.72,0:05:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.76,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.53,0:05:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是钓鱼的叔叔\N他常常钓到很多鱼哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔  叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.51,0:05:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞上来的人是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.41,0:05:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们叫你拿钱道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是非常有钱吗  小少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.22,0:05:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命呀 谁来救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的刀子不见了  跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.71,0:06:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.85,0:06:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么快速又利落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.42,0:06:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那男人若是拿刀的话\N他…到底是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.96,0:06:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是怎么回事 遇到妖怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.50,0:06:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是他们同伴吗\N这只老山羊 可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二次再这样我可不放过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔  叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在哭呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.26,0:07:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次不是约定好的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.77,0:07:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你那样子似乎挺辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.48,0:07:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要来吗  我知道一个绝佳场所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.08,0:07:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.03,0:07:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最好的钓鱼日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.27,0:07:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老先生你很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是何时放弃杀人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.81,0:07:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是头次遇见象你这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.75,0:07:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时具备温和与强烈\N 两种极端剑气的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.75,0:08:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老先生您什么都看出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.69,0:08:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个抛弃獠牙的剑客呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.49,0:08:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会在这里碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.86,0:08:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是过于漫长的人生中\N有某种缘份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过于漫长？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.00,0:08:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾在初夏夜晚来这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一片望去都是萤火虫呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫做许愿萤火虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.21,0:08:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,许愿萤火虫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩 人们是这么称呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.25,0:08:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在江户时代\N还没结束的很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.68,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位现在已经年老的男人\N还充满希望的年代的故事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.73,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的刀法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.37,0:08:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不出来才17岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.74,0:08:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 您又得冠军了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.85,0:09:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江户虽大 可是我觉得龙之助\N你已经天下无敌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.65,0:09:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说下次您要在将军面前\N做示范赛 是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个我拒绝了 无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.72,0:09:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.19,0:09:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我厌倦现在的我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那股厌倦感一日比一日强烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.67,0:09:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想变得更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是竹刀无法满足我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.21,0:09:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武士必需拿真刀搏命\N才可能达到真正厉害的境界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经很强了呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.15,0:09:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想追求最强的终极境界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.26,0:09:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你朋友？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.23,0:09:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我姐啦 都跟你介绍过好几次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 快过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.48,0:10:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 你什么也没注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道许愿萤火虫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.62,0:10:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说只要全年不休\N每天都到那里祈祷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.76,0:10:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初夏时候\N萤火虫就会达成那个人的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.53,0:10:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐连续来两个月了\N想要龙之助了解她的心意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.04,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女人叫做阿娟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人犹豫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.18,0:10:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然犹豫 但还是渐渐接受了阿绢的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.18,0:10:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位专注剑道的男人身上\N点起了微微的光亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.05,0:10:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,象萤火虫一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在后来不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.32,0:10:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光明转为黑暗的命运日子到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强盗呀 大家快来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.99,0:11:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.51,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那简直是雷神之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.18,0:11:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由被杀的三人神情可看出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.05,0:11:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是瞬间毙命\N没察觉自己已被杀死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.45,0:12:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人兴奋得战栗了\N这才是剑的极致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.06,0:12:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只在真正过招\N决生死的一刹那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.90,0:12:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能找到真正的究极
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.55,0:12:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一夜 男人首次杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后在隔天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 不是真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙之助你杀了人了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要抛弃这个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.75,0:13:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算让我的剑染满鲜血\N我也要钻研出究极的剑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.55,0:13:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙之助 不行 不可以 杀人是不对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.66,0:13:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.43,0:13:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你坚持要再杀人\N就请先杀我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.78,0:13:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.02,0:13:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那天开始 男人一再杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他眼中没看到被他杀死的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.56,0:13:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一味追逐那天晚上\N他看到的究极之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.60,0:13:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对 那天晚上我看到的剑法\N不是这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对 还是不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.06,0:14:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年 十五年了\N他一直在迷惘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.36,0:14:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对 离究极还很远\N我到底是缺少什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第21年的某个傍晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感到绝望的男人\N甚至起了自杀念头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.07,0:15:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强盗 谁来救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.48,0:15:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他忘不了的\N暴风雨夜的那个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.16,0:15:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他发觉时 他已经拔剑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.41,0:16:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那神情…一点痛楚也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.88,0:16:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表示他是瞬间毙命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.28,0:16:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人知道了\N他早已超越了究极的剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.09,0:16:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对 究极这东西\N打一开始就不存在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.33,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在暴风雨中他看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.43,0:16:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是潜伏心中\N黑暗处的幻影罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.75,0:16:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人从漫长的梦中清醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.06,0:17:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人的沉重罪恶感\N把男人压得几乎崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.88,0:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样做…怎样做才能赎罪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.95,0:17:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁来教教我 谁来教教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.28,0:17:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教教我…教教我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙之助 龙之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.80,0:18:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.83,0:18:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于结束了\N漫长的灵魂之旅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.85,0:18:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你 等了好久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.52,0:19:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到21年前那地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是旅行者吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.93,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是听到\N许愿萤火虫的传说的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的姐姐一直在等待某个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.87,0:19:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信那个人\N一定会回来在这里许愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.57,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20年来 她每天在这里等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是姐姐的忌日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.60,0:19:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 龙之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.90,0:20:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不离开你 永远地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.08,0:20:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是许愿萤火虫的故事\N好几十年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,许愿萤火虫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.24,0:20:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.41,0:20:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经这么晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要回去啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要当乖小孩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天要再来哦 就这么约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.35,0:20:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以问一个问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.76,0:20:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人的人生有悔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.57,0:21:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算后悔 也无法从头再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.34,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.24,0:21:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那男人遇见生涯之中\N唯一一个无法忘怀的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.01,0:21:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很想让那女人象萤火虫一样\N短暂的生命光辉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.92,0:21:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停留在别人心中片刻\N而不只是停留在自己心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.23,0:21:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你听我讲这么长的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想以后是不会再见到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家 剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.89,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了啦 剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.52,0:22:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.16,0:22:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有钓到鱼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.13,0:22:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 一条鱼也没钓到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.63,0:22:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的\N玄斋先生把菜拿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.04,0:22:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 小绫跟小雀都饿了吧\N我们来吃饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.01,0:22:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭了
